{"tid":2268583,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"青年涉去年西灣河堵路 罪名不成立","createTime":"2020-11-03T02:21:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T09:48:47.000Z","uid":240362,"like":75,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"1bb2e39367afedc6fe7db2ef3550e383e09b865b","tid":2268583,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T02:21:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10886\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F10886&d=tGWxp70K68wBh01xS7f0EsbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=27482045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10886</a><br />\n<br />\n#東區裁判法院第八庭<br />\n#黃雅茵裁判官<br />\n#1113西灣河 #裁決 <br />\n<br />\n鄧(20) <br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n在公眾地方造成阻礙 <br />\n<br />\n案情：<br />\n於去年11月13日與其他身份不詳人士在筲箕灣道與成安街交界，無合法權限下留下磚頭和垃圾，對上述地點的人或車輛造成阻礙、不便或危害 <br />\n<br />\n法庭認為PW1證供有多處前後矛盾及不合理<br />\n1) 逃跑的示威者人數有3個不同版本<br />\n2) 被告站(庭上) 及逃跑(口供)時掉磚<br />\n3) 認同被告背囊是重要特徵但口供卻沒提及<br />\n4) 指幾十名示威者由筲箕灣道向PW1及5名警員方向逃跑不合理 <br />\n<br />\n因此不接納PW1的證供<br />\n<br />\n被告罪名不成立🎉"},{"pid":"9ae33c8ad97786983076bc8b7f6c71213ae3415e","tid":2268583,"uid":79793,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T02:22:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">還我公義</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9f85544f57e34dbdda2171c5ceac3d061d277f25","tid":2268583,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T02:26:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"867139df6da780c867c5e70baea6a280164dd8fe","tid":2268583,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T03:02:15.000Z","msg":"男子被控去年11月三罷期間在西灣河一帶堵路，罪名不成立。裁判官指，警員證供前後矛盾。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官黃雅茵稱，本案第一證人，即拘捕被告的警員，證供前後矛盾，對當時情況的記憶並不肯定，而本案最大爭議點是被告的身份，供詞未能證明被告有份拋下石頭並參與堵路，在疑點利益歸於被告下，裁定被告罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=411414\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D411414&d=tGWxp70K68wBh01xS7f0EsbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=da33409b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D411414&h=dcaecc59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=411414</a>"},{"pid":"c9058cb14aa7c275a6afc4cb7c9819a1ca4ad058","tid":2268583,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T03:43:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbcb47b3496a2b296a4cda4671b6802b2f026289","tid":2268583,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T03:44:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"024ffd0c12d86bd8c5a519741382aed6a9357fad","tid":2268583,"uid":132810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T03:45:17.000Z","msg":"好消息"},{"pid":"4344d568d9d2f1eab573d5ac3ce66224f2dd1a59","tid":2268583,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T04:11:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"715b7c072030177963c4a72a0e8695dc74d65255","tid":2268583,"uid":49329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T04:12:45.000Z","msg":"正常判決"},{"pid":"36bc8b1d17087ca0c40e95b64feb1ad8a9e892cc","tid":2268583,"uid":80503,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T04:13:53.000Z","msg":"指幾十名示威者由筲箕灣道向PW1及5名警員方向逃跑不合理 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以為佢地同班黑警玩緊紅綠燈"},{"pid":"eed6f70079fd964